<lb n="0491b25"/><head type="no">No. 1329</head><div1 type="dharani">
<lb n="0491b26"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0491024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說&CB00057;小兒<note n="0491025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（東晉西域三藏竺曇無蘭譯）十一字譯號【元】【明】</note><app n="0491025"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">經東晉西域三藏竺曇無蘭譯</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0491b27"/>
<lb n="0491b28"/><p type="dharani">羅那多羅　摩羅提離　耽波羅提利　吼樓
<lb n="0491b29"/>壽　無樓壽　聞闍　輂叉輂差</p><p place="inline">南無佛南
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1329.0491c" n="0491c"/>
<lb n="0491c01"/>無法南無比丘僧南無過去七佛南無諸佛南
<lb n="0491c02"/>無諸佛弟子　令我所&CB00057;即從如願。若小兒
<lb n="0491c03"/>頭痛腹痛。當說七<note n="0491026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝遍【三】</note><note n="0491026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＝遍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491026"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">遍</rdg></app>即愈</p>
<lb n="0491c04"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說&CB00057;小兒經</jhead></juan></div1>
